--- !u!114 &9092312783662962029
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 6672811681591886674}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 47bbad0787e383b49aa5c035a854673b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data: FUNFACT
  strings:
  - The currency was originally called Battle-Bucks, however it didn't feel monke
    enough.
  - The backpacks for switching teams, were originally used for switching colours.
  - You can go through most posters in the Battle Royale map.
  - This game will statistically speaking, blow up.
  - You can't level up in private lobbies.
  - When a game is running, you will not matchmake to that game.
  - There are secrets everywhere!
  - There is a very low chance you're reading this.
  - It took around half a year to go from idea to release!
  - For now the day bleeds!
  - Cross-teaming is NOT allowed.
  - Teaming in Solos is a bannable offense.
